1339
01:22:52,560 --> 01:22:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] ne konzumiraš vijesti

1340
01:22:53,359 --> 01:22:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] spada kvore se ima neki asketa

1341
01:22:54,920 --> 01:22:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji odlučuje da to neće raditi.

1342
01:22:56,340 --> 01:22:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je lako ne konzumirati vijesti.

1343
01:22:58,239 --> 01:22:59,399
[SPEAKER_00] Probodim se ovo jutro,

1344
01:22:59,399 --> 01:23:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] gdje da ću im vijesti?

1345
01:23:01,060 --> 01:23:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] krenem na svoj put,

1346
01:23:01,880 --> 01:23:02,560
[SPEAKER_00] na svoje stvari,

1347
01:23:02,560 --> 01:23:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] kroz dar,

1348
01:23:03,000 --> 01:23:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] gdje da ću im vijesti?

1349
01:23:04,079 --> 01:23:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ne gledam nevnik,

1350
01:23:05,359 --> 01:23:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] gdje da ću im vijesti?

1351
01:23:06,300 --> 01:23:07,260
[SPEAKER_00] Na internet,

1352
01:23:07,260 --> 01:23:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne palim ove,

1353
01:23:08,380 --> 01:23:09,739
[SPEAKER_00] gdje da ću im vijesti?

1354
01:23:09,739 --> 01:23:10,979
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto to ljudi rade?

1355
01:23:10,979 --> 01:23:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

1356
01:23:11,640 --> 01:23:12,939
[SPEAKER_00] Pa znaš kaj,

1357
01:23:12,939 --> 01:23:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] mogu ti reći zašto rade?

1358
01:23:14,159 --> 01:23:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] Možda po jednom svom iskustvu.

1359
01:23:16,720 --> 01:23:18,439
[SPEAKER_00] i by the way,

1360
01:23:18,439 --> 01:23:20,060
[SPEAKER_00] opet aglicizam

1361
01:23:20,060 --> 01:23:21,300
[SPEAKER_00] za tvoje gledatelje,

1362
01:23:21,300 --> 01:23:23,560
[SPEAKER_00] ipak informacije dođe do mene.

1363
01:23:23,560 --> 01:23:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

1364
01:23:23,880 --> 01:23:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kupujem duha na kiosku,

1365
01:23:25,039 --> 01:23:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] padne mi pogled na naslov.

1366
01:23:26,539 --> 01:23:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] Hodam tamo,

1367
01:23:27,680 --> 01:23:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] nekom je lese i vidio ovo i ono.

1368
01:23:29,039 --> 01:23:30,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ti zapravo sve znam što se zbiva.

1369
01:23:30,439 --> 01:23:31,100
[SPEAKER_00] Bitno,

1370
01:23:31,100 --> 01:23:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] a da uopće ne pratim vijesti.

1371
01:23:32,159 --> 01:23:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nekako uz put čujem.

1372
01:23:33,319 --> 01:23:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ali se sjećam

1373
01:23:35,800 --> 01:23:38,479
[SPEAKER_00] kakva je to može biti ovisnost.

1374
01:23:38,479 --> 01:23:39,520
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kad sam počeo raditi

1375
01:23:39,520 --> 01:23:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] u obrazovnom i vječjem programu

1376
01:23:40,920 --> 01:23:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatskog radija,

1377
01:23:42,119 --> 01:23:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] gdje sam bio surne kod 93.

1378
01:23:43,340 --> 01:23:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kasnije 96. sam kao bio zaposleno.

1379
01:23:46,239 --> 01:23:47,479
[SPEAKER_00] Cijelo vrijeme to sam radio

1380
01:23:47,479 --> 01:23:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] dječju emisiju o sportu,

1381
01:23:48,619 --> 01:23:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] pun pogodak,

1382
01:23:49,279 --> 01:23:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] neke emisije o obrazovanju.

1383
01:23:50,760 --> 01:23:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja i tada nisam čito novio nikad.

1384
01:23:53,000 --> 01:23:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Me to nije zanimalo.

1385
01:23:53,880 --> 01:23:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] I bio sam totalni zapravo neznalica.

1386
01:23:55,960 --> 01:23:57,140
[SPEAKER_00] I sad to šljakak.

1387
01:23:57,140 --> 01:23:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja radim priloge o obrazovanju,

1388
01:23:58,920 --> 01:23:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] snimih i tak dalje.

1389
01:23:59,840 --> 01:24:01,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sad je bilo ono,

1390
01:24:01,100 --> 01:24:02,359
[SPEAKER_00] joj, bio ovaj

1391
01:24:02,359 --> 01:24:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] skeaš tomba.

1392
01:24:03,659 --> 01:24:04,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je taj tombe?

1393
01:24:04,859 --> 01:24:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ova,

1394
01:24:05,739 --> 01:24:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] nekakav mon senior neki je nešto radio.

1395
01:24:08,579 --> 01:24:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam svega pitam,

1396
01:24:10,079 --> 01:24:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam bio glup,

1397
01:24:10,659 --> 01:24:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] pa sam još to i pokazivo,

1398
01:24:11,640 --> 01:24:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] da nema pojma.

1399
01:24:12,220 --> 01:24:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam misla,

1400
01:24:13,220 --> 01:24:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja ne znam da je to neki nepoznat čovjek.

1401
01:24:15,239 --> 01:24:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je taj,

1402
01:24:16,180 --> 01:24:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] i krivo ga izgovorim,

1403
01:24:17,199 --> 01:24:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] dok mi nije tadašnja urednica rekla,

1404
01:24:18,920 --> 01:24:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] gledaj,

1405
01:24:19,260 --> 01:24:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] ti si sramota za novinarsku profesiju

1406
01:24:21,739 --> 01:24:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] i sad imaš domaću zaraču.

1407
01:24:24,119 --> 01:24:26,100
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan izvoli pročitaj novine.

1408
01:24:26,100 --> 01:24:27,939
[SPEAKER_00] I tad sam ja po zadatku,

1409
01:24:27,939 --> 01:24:29,359
[SPEAKER_00] svaki dan kad sam došao u redakciju,

1410
01:24:29,359 --> 01:24:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] uzao, ne znam,

1411
01:24:30,079 --> 01:24:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] veće neće kaj je već bilo

1412
01:24:31,239 --> 01:24:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] i čitao novine.

1413
01:24:32,399 --> 01:24:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] I mogu te reći,

1414
01:24:33,899 --> 01:24:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] bilo jako zanimljivo.

1415
01:24:35,279 --> 01:24:36,479
[SPEAKER_00] I ne samo to.

1416
01:24:36,479 --> 01:24:37,359
[SPEAKER_00] Onda bih pročitao,

1417
01:24:37,359 --> 01:24:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] onda drugi dan dođem

1418
01:24:38,340 --> 01:24:40,100
[SPEAKER_00] i će čitati šta se dalje zbio.

1419
01:24:40,100 --> 01:24:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] Eto ti jedna trakavica

1420
01:24:41,300 --> 01:24:41,939
[SPEAKER_00] i ti zapravo ćeš

1421
01:24:41,939 --> 01:24:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] on ti stalno isto ponavljaju,

1422
01:24:43,079 --> 01:24:43,939
[SPEAKER_00] pa ti sam učitaš.

1423
01:24:43,939 --> 01:24:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] I bilo mi jako zanimljivo.

1424
01:24:44,840 --> 01:24:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaj, sve što se navučeš

1425
01:24:46,300 --> 01:24:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] kone serije o kojoj bih sam ti pričao,

1426
01:24:47,720 --> 01:24:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] su zanimljile.

1427
01:24:48,199 --> 01:24:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] Onda kad se skineš njih,

1428
01:24:49,840 --> 01:24:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] onda jednostavno shvatiš

1429
01:24:51,239 --> 01:24:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] kako si bio obuzet.

1430
01:24:52,600 --> 01:24:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja vjerujem

1431
01:24:53,300 --> 01:24:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] da je to jako jedna sapunica.

1432
01:24:54,579 --> 01:24:55,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ti uđeš u to,

1433
01:24:55,479 --> 01:24:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] pa šta ima dalje?

1434
01:24:56,220 --> 01:24:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa te privuče.

1435
01:24:56,880 --> 01:24:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] Meni istorica mu privuče,

1436
01:24:57,779 --> 01:24:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] kada nego kre mene upali,

1437
01:24:59,279 --> 01:24:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

1438
01:24:59,600 --> 01:25:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] danas je to više nije papirati mediju,

1439
01:25:01,279 --> 01:25:02,760
[SPEAKER_00] uglavnom je pametni telefon.

1440
01:25:02,760 --> 01:25:03,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ti sam neka vijest,

1441
01:25:03,600 --> 01:25:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] daj, pogled ovo.

1442
01:25:04,420 --> 01:25:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja daj, pogled u Španijskoj poplo.

1443
01:25:06,500 --> 01:25:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam uči čuo za to.

1444
01:25:07,500 --> 01:25:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da onda dođem,

1445
01:25:08,460 --> 01:25:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] ja čekaj da vidim šta se dozbiva.

1446
01:25:09,840 --> 01:25:11,520
[SPEAKER_00] O, vidi kako su otišle kuće.

1447
01:25:12,100 --> 01:25:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zanimljivo je, kužiš.

1448
01:25:14,880 --> 01:25:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Zato jer je, ono,

1449
01:25:16,500 --> 01:25:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] katastrofično je.

1450
01:25:17,800 --> 01:25:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što ljudi vole.

1451
01:25:18,460 --> 01:25:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] Nemati tamo vijesti u smislu,

1452
01:25:20,300 --> 01:25:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to nepoznati komičar,

1453
01:25:22,760 --> 01:25:24,899
[SPEAKER_00] rekao one koje uvijek ima duhovne neke sadržaje.

1454
01:25:24,899 --> 01:25:25,439
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, rekao je,

1455
01:25:25,439 --> 01:25:28,399
[SPEAKER_00] u vijestima vam piše da je poplava odnjela pola zemlja,

1456
01:25:28,399 --> 01:25:33,020
[SPEAKER_00] a neće vam pisati da je Vinko doživio prosvjetljenje u Bostonu, kužiš.

1457
01:25:33,020 --> 01:25:34,399
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to kao nije bitna vijest.

1458
01:25:34,399 --> 01:25:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zato je jako bitna vijest da je nekoj dijete palo kroz prozoru u Engleskoj.

1459
01:25:37,699 --> 01:25:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako bitna vijest.

1460
01:25:38,779 --> 01:25:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] Za cijelu hrvatsku naciju.

1461
01:25:40,319 --> 01:25:41,520
[SPEAKER_00] I onda mi o tom čitamo.

1462
01:25:41,520 --> 01:25:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da u tom kontekstu,

1463
01:25:43,159 --> 01:25:44,399
[SPEAKER_00] M sam dovoljno informiran,

1464
01:25:44,399 --> 01:25:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] M razumijem kako se ljudi navuku na to ovisnosti.

1465
01:25:47,380 --> 01:25:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki čovjek koji je malo razmišljao,

1466
01:25:49,579 --> 01:25:50,979
[SPEAKER_00] je drugima savjetovo.

1467
01:25:50,979 --> 01:25:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ako želiš,

1468
01:25:52,079 --> 01:25:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] neki boljitak samom sebi.

1469
01:25:54,159 --> 01:25:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi zadovoljno samom.

1470
01:25:55,220 --> 01:25:57,680
[SPEAKER_00] Nervozan si, pod stresom si.

1471
01:25:57,680 --> 01:25:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znaš šta da napraviš.

1472
01:25:59,159 --> 01:26:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kreni od najjednostavnije stvari.

1473
01:26:01,239 --> 01:26:02,319
[SPEAKER_00] Za početak,

1474
01:26:02,319 --> 01:26:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno nemoj gledati nikakvu vijest

1475
01:26:06,239 --> 01:26:09,520
[SPEAKER_00] uđi u abstinenciju barem na koji dan.

1476
01:26:09,520 --> 01:26:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] I doćiš do zanimljive spoznaje.

1477
01:26:13,140 --> 01:26:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon dva, tri, četiri dana.

1478
01:26:14,800 --> 01:26:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] Više ti se neće dati upalit nijedno.

1479
01:26:17,319 --> 01:26:18,479
[SPEAKER_00] Kuž.

1480
01:26:18,479 --> 01:26:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] I to je dosta dobar prostor za čovjek,

1481
01:26:20,619 --> 01:26:21,939
[SPEAKER_00] jer kuž, dok ti razmišljaš u vijestima,

1482
01:26:21,939 --> 01:26:23,600
[SPEAKER_00] ti si tamo negdje sa svješću.

1483
01:26:23,600 --> 01:26:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo se zbiva u stvari.

1484
01:26:24,739 --> 01:26:25,779
[SPEAKER_00] A ništa se tamo ne zbiva.

1485
01:26:25,779 --> 01:26:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, zamisli da nema novine televizije.

1486
01:26:28,760 --> 01:26:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] Šta? Evo, pogledaj.

1487
01:26:31,659 --> 01:26:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je problem?

1488
01:26:33,500 --> 01:26:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo ti zanimljivo istraživanje o tome

1489
01:26:35,220 --> 01:26:37,819
[SPEAKER_00] kako se, ko ima više straha?

1490
01:26:37,819 --> 01:26:40,560
[SPEAKER_00] Djece, dječak i djete koje žive u Njurku

1491
01:26:40,560 --> 01:26:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] ili djete koji živi tamo,

1492
01:26:42,319 --> 01:26:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo pre 30-40 godina na Bliskom istoku.

1493
01:26:44,260 --> 01:26:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ali priča je dalje aktualna.

1494
01:26:45,300 --> 01:26:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] Bliski istok je uvijek bio turbulentan.

1495
01:26:47,119 --> 01:26:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] Što se ispostavilo?

1496
01:26:49,220 --> 01:26:51,180
[SPEAKER_00] Da, američki, njurški klinac

1497
01:26:51,180 --> 01:26:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] ima puno veći strah od svijeta.

1498
01:26:53,319 --> 01:26:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] Mada je on u sigurnom okružu svog stana

1499
01:26:55,680 --> 01:26:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] idu u školu, ništa mu se ne zbiva,

1500
01:26:57,159 --> 01:26:58,560
[SPEAKER_00] ali on stalno kroz vijesti,

1501
01:26:58,560 --> 01:27:00,060
[SPEAKER_00] gleda kako tamo bombe,

1502
01:27:00,060 --> 01:27:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] poput resi ovo ono.

1503
01:27:01,159 --> 01:27:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] A dječak, njegov vršnjak,

1504
01:27:03,199 --> 01:27:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] koji živi u područjima gdje zaista

1505
01:27:05,300 --> 01:27:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] ono, rat, ruševine, nešto se zbiva,

1506
01:27:08,680 --> 01:27:10,279
[SPEAKER_00] on ima puno manji strah.

1507
01:27:10,279 --> 01:27:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Nije izložen medijima.

1508
01:27:11,800 --> 01:27:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, eksplodira bomba tamo

1509
01:27:13,359 --> 01:27:14,279
[SPEAKER_00] na drugom kraju Beruta.

1510
01:27:14,279 --> 01:27:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam tu i nisam je čuo.

1511
01:27:16,579 --> 01:27:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je eksplodirala u sekundi

1512
01:27:17,880 --> 01:27:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] i više nije eksplodirala, gotova je.

1513
01:27:19,619 --> 01:27:21,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi se rekla?

1514
01:27:21,359 --> 01:27:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti nemaš nakon toga

1515
01:27:22,220 --> 01:27:23,260
[SPEAKER_00] deset dana bombardiranja

1516
01:27:23,260 --> 01:27:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] o bombi kroz novine,

1517
01:27:24,180 --> 01:27:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo taj klinac će imati

1518
01:27:26,420 --> 01:27:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] puno manje straha

1519
01:27:27,199 --> 01:27:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] jer živi samo unutar svijeta

1520
01:27:28,359 --> 01:27:29,520
[SPEAKER_00] koji sam može dosegnuti

1521
01:27:29,520 --> 01:27:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] svojim osjeteljima

1522
01:27:30,340 --> 01:27:31,600
[SPEAKER_00] i on će biti u strahu

1523
01:27:31,600 --> 01:27:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] eventualno od onog što se tu zbiva.

1524
01:27:32,960 --> 01:27:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mi danas čitamo o ratovima

1525
01:27:36,239 --> 01:27:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] u novinama,

1526
01:27:36,880 --> 01:27:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] o svim ti drugim stvarima

1527
01:27:38,000 --> 01:27:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] i misle o kako je opasno

1528
01:27:39,159 --> 01:27:39,939
[SPEAKER_00] svijet ti je u ratu.

1529
01:27:39,939 --> 01:27:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali čekaj, prestani čitat.

1530
01:27:41,119 --> 01:27:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nećeš ni znat da je rat.

1531
01:27:43,199 --> 01:27:44,520
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kaže,

1532
01:27:44,520 --> 01:27:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] to nije humano.

1533
01:27:45,640 --> 01:27:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ma šta nije humano?

1534
01:27:46,720 --> 01:27:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pa se sjećam kada je bio rat u Hrvatskoj

1535
01:27:48,119 --> 01:27:48,859
[SPEAKER_00] pa su ljudi govorili,

1536
01:27:48,859 --> 01:27:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] niko ne mari što je tu rat,

1537
01:27:50,739 --> 01:27:52,279
[SPEAKER_00] kako svijet ne mari.

1538
01:27:52,279 --> 01:27:53,020
[SPEAKER_00] A ja sam si mislil,

1539
01:27:53,020 --> 01:27:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] pa zašto bi svijet mario?

1540
01:27:54,220 --> 01:27:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne bi nija mario za rat u Belgiji.

1541
01:27:56,079 --> 01:27:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] Šta me briga?

1542
01:27:57,279 --> 01:27:58,520
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju kraja svako dobi

1543
01:27:58,520 --> 01:27:59,979
[SPEAKER_00] svoju porciju rata prili kasnije.

1544
01:27:59,979 --> 01:28:02,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi se reklo ono?

1545
01:28:02,880 --> 01:28:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da manjak tih informacija

1546
01:28:06,159 --> 01:28:07,939
[SPEAKER_00] predstavlja višak dobrobiti za čovjek.

1547
01:28:07,939 --> 01:28:13,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je još jedno od pitanja od publike.

1548
01:28:13,119 --> 01:28:16,279
[SPEAKER_01] Viruješ li u Boga?

1549
01:28:16,279 --> 01:28:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta, najjednostavniji mi je odgovor

1550
01:28:19,880 --> 01:28:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudima kažem ne.

1551
01:28:20,800 --> 01:28:21,979
[SPEAKER_00] Da me ne gnjave.

1552
01:28:21,979 --> 01:28:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da stvar nije tako kompleksna

1553
01:28:25,840 --> 01:28:29,819
[SPEAKER_00] zato jer na meniju imaš premalo tih mogućnosti.

1554
01:28:29,819 --> 01:28:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ti danas možeš biti ateist,

1555
01:28:32,039 --> 01:28:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] to nekoj ne vjeruje u Boga,

1556
01:28:32,960 --> 01:28:34,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego sve je materija.

1557
01:28:34,039 --> 01:28:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš biti naravno vjernik,

1558
01:28:35,960 --> 01:28:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] bilo koje religije koje vjeruju u Boga

1559
01:28:38,840 --> 01:28:41,640
[SPEAKER_00] i možeš biti takozvani agnostik.

1560
01:28:41,640 --> 01:28:43,399
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ti kao ima nešto,

1561
01:28:43,399 --> 01:28:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti ne znaš to,

1562
01:28:44,119 --> 01:28:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi se šteli mešati,

1563
01:28:45,000 --> 01:28:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi se reklo.

1564
01:28:45,739 --> 01:28:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] I to ti meni baš jedno

1565
01:28:47,640 --> 01:28:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] čer pitalo svoje dobro,

1566
01:28:48,819 --> 01:28:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo jasno.

1567
01:28:49,300 --> 01:28:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš ti vjernik.

1568
01:28:50,159 --> 01:28:51,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nju vjerujem, gledaj.

1569
01:28:51,100 --> 01:28:52,180
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš to, to i to.

1570
01:28:52,180 --> 01:28:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] A ja nisam jasno ti doživljenik.

1571
01:28:53,619 --> 01:28:54,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ona ode.

1572
01:28:55,619 --> 01:28:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da se vrati,

1573
01:28:56,619 --> 01:28:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] ta reč postoji li si ti izmislio?

1574
01:28:58,760 --> 01:29:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa izmislio sam,

1575
01:29:00,199 --> 01:29:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali moramo izmisliti nove reči

1576
01:29:01,159 --> 01:29:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] za nove sadržaje.

1577
01:29:02,000 --> 01:29:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj, te po nove reči.

1578
01:29:03,000 --> 01:29:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] Doživljenik.

1579
01:29:03,699 --> 01:29:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Doživljenik.

1580
01:29:04,539 --> 01:29:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] Pa i ti si doživljenik.

1581
01:29:06,539 --> 01:29:07,119
[SPEAKER_00] Kojiše, pazi,

1582
01:29:07,119 --> 01:29:08,899
[SPEAKER_00] dogod si ti u sveri ja i Bog,

1583
01:29:08,899 --> 01:29:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] ti si još uvijek u sveri dualizma.

1584
01:29:11,039 --> 01:29:13,439
[SPEAKER_00] Kojiš, ti vjerujš u Boga,

1585
01:29:13,439 --> 01:29:14,939
[SPEAKER_00] on tebe gleda dvojeste.

1586
01:29:14,939 --> 01:29:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] Na tebljnoj razini nema dualizma.

1587
01:29:16,739 --> 01:29:19,100
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, postoji samo ja koji doživljavam

1588
01:29:19,100 --> 01:29:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] i niko drugi.

1589
01:29:19,939 --> 01:29:21,640
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, je li ja vjerujem u Boga

1590
01:29:21,640 --> 01:29:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne vjerujem, nemam pojma.

1591
01:29:22,579 --> 01:29:23,899
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno ne znam.

1592
01:29:23,899 --> 01:29:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovim konceptima

1593
01:29:25,539 --> 01:29:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] o kojima sam do sad čuo

1594
01:29:26,500 --> 01:29:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] da se pričao u tom kontekstu, ne.

1595
01:29:27,880 --> 01:29:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, sad bi neko rekao,

1596
01:29:30,560 --> 01:29:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali pazi,

1597
01:29:31,180 --> 01:29:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam miljama daleko

1598
01:29:32,760 --> 01:29:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] od nekog ateista

1599
01:29:34,079 --> 01:29:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili nekog ko vjeruje u slučaj,

1600
01:29:35,380 --> 01:29:36,699
[SPEAKER_00] jer vidim da je svijet

1601
01:29:36,699 --> 01:29:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] duboko usklađen.

1602
01:29:37,760 --> 01:29:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da svaki organizam,

1603
01:29:39,739 --> 01:29:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje tijelo,

1604
01:29:40,380 --> 01:29:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] biljke, drveće,

1605
01:29:42,000 --> 01:29:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] da sve imaju odlike

1606
01:29:43,920 --> 01:29:45,819
[SPEAKER_00] sustavane u manjive složnosti.

1607
01:29:45,819 --> 01:29:46,659
[SPEAKER_00] Da je morao iza svega

1608
01:29:46,659 --> 01:29:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] biti ideal i nacrt.

1609
01:29:47,659 --> 01:29:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

1610
01:29:48,380 --> 01:29:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] ako ovaj svijet nije materialan,

1611
01:29:50,300 --> 01:29:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] onda se ne moramo zamarati

1612
01:29:52,039 --> 01:29:53,159
[SPEAKER_00] ko je njegov tvorac.

1613
01:29:53,159 --> 01:29:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] Tvorac smo je one

1614
01:29:53,880 --> 01:29:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] koga izmišlja.

1615
01:29:54,699 --> 01:29:56,180
[SPEAKER_00] A to bi bio ti,

1616
01:29:56,180 --> 01:29:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili ja,

1617
01:29:56,699 --> 01:29:57,439
[SPEAKER_00] ili neko drugi.

1618
01:29:57,439 --> 01:29:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja tako u tom kontekstu

1619
01:29:59,079 --> 01:29:59,800
[SPEAKER_00] i ne vjerujem u Boga.

1620
01:29:59,800 --> 01:30:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] Istvarno,

1621
01:30:01,159 --> 01:30:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] zatikvelim,

1622
01:30:01,619 --> 01:30:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] nikad mi niko nije

1623
01:30:02,579 --> 01:30:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] mogu objasniti

1624
01:30:03,319 --> 01:30:03,979
[SPEAKER_00] šta je to Bog,

1625
01:30:03,979 --> 01:30:04,600
[SPEAKER_00] pa da bi se mogu

1626
01:30:04,600 --> 01:30:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] prema tome odrediti.

1627
01:30:05,500 --> 01:30:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] To ste jedan abstrakti pojam.

1628
01:30:08,239 --> 01:30:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda ljudi kažu,

1629
01:30:09,000 --> 01:30:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je ljubav.

1630
01:30:10,619 --> 01:30:11,899
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, šta je ljubav?

1631
01:30:11,899 --> 01:30:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] A šta je Bog?

1632
01:30:12,800 --> 01:30:15,239
[SPEAKER_00] Definicije sa pojmima

1633
01:30:15,239 --> 01:30:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] koje nisu razrešeni.

1634
01:30:16,159 --> 01:30:17,560
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

1635
01:30:17,560 --> 01:30:17,819
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

1636
01:30:17,819 --> 01:30:19,100
[SPEAKER_00] s krativom priču kažem da ne,

1637
01:30:19,100 --> 01:30:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] ali kao što vidimo,

1638
01:30:19,779 --> 01:30:21,319
[SPEAKER_00] priča je malo kompleksnije.

1639
01:30:22,079 --> 01:30:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] Jel ti vjerujš u Boga?

1640
01:30:23,800 --> 01:30:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem,

1641
01:30:31,760 --> 01:30:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja vjerujem,

1642
01:30:32,300 --> 01:30:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja vjerujem,

1643
01:30:33,300 --> 01:30:35,640
[SPEAKER_01] ja vjerujem u om.

1644
01:30:35,640 --> 01:30:38,640
[SPEAKER_01] Istražujem,

1645
01:30:38,640 --> 01:30:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] rekao bi da istražujem.

1646
01:30:40,079 --> 01:30:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] Još uvijek nisam zaključio.

1647
01:30:41,380 --> 01:30:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] A ti misliš

1648
01:30:42,779 --> 01:30:44,439
[SPEAKER_00] da se vjera u Boga

1649
01:30:44,439 --> 01:30:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] temelji na racionalnom zaključivanju?

1650
01:30:47,119 --> 01:30:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] A zašto ti misliš

1651
01:30:48,300 --> 01:30:49,600
[SPEAKER_01] da ja istražujem racionalno?

1652
01:30:49,600 --> 01:30:50,600
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

1653
01:30:50,600 --> 01:30:53,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dokad misliš istraživati?

1654
01:30:53,159 --> 01:30:55,939
[SPEAKER_00] Dok se ponovno ne rodim.

1655
01:30:55,939 --> 01:30:56,859
[SPEAKER_00] Aha, znači,

1656
01:30:56,859 --> 01:30:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] ti uopće nemaš namir

1657
01:30:57,659 --> 01:30:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] odgovora na to pitanje,

1658
01:30:58,500 --> 01:30:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] nikad?

1659
01:30:58,859 --> 01:30:59,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

1660
01:30:59,680 --> 01:31:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda šta ko reci?

1661
01:31:01,500 --> 01:31:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] Reci, neću ti reći,

1662
01:31:03,140 --> 01:31:04,100
[SPEAKER_00] a ne istražujem.

1663
01:31:04,100 --> 01:31:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne,

1664
01:31:04,460 --> 01:31:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] rekao sam ti,

1665
01:31:05,380 --> 01:31:06,279
[SPEAKER_01] iskreno sam ti rekao,

1666
01:31:06,279 --> 01:31:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] istražujem i dalje.

1667
01:31:07,079 --> 01:31:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] To je odgovor,

1668
01:31:07,859 --> 01:31:08,859
[SPEAKER_00] ja misli da je poštini odgovor

1669
01:31:08,859 --> 01:31:09,399
[SPEAKER_00] na to pitanje,

1670
01:31:09,399 --> 01:31:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam.

1671
01:31:09,760 --> 01:31:11,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne znam,

1672
01:31:11,420 --> 01:31:12,399
[SPEAKER_01] istražujem i dalje.

1673
01:31:12,399 --> 01:31:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1674
01:31:17,119 --> 01:31:17,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mislimo ne.

1675
01:31:17,380 --> 01:31:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1676
01:31:17,960 --> 01:31:19,100
[SPEAKER_01] Odustao si.

1677
01:31:19,100 --> 01:31:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam odustao.

1678
01:31:20,119 --> 01:31:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam se nikad i pitao.

1679
01:31:21,340 --> 01:31:23,420
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam i počeo.

1680
01:31:23,420 --> 01:31:24,140
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

1681
01:31:24,140 --> 01:31:25,939
[SPEAKER_01] Nedavno si,

1682
01:31:25,939 --> 01:31:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] malo prije si mi

1683
01:31:26,800 --> 01:31:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] imao

1684
01:31:29,800 --> 01:31:31,600
[SPEAKER_01] onakvu reakciju

1685
01:31:31,600 --> 01:31:32,520
[SPEAKER_01] kad si spomenio

1686
01:31:32,520 --> 01:31:33,760
[SPEAKER_01] riječ duhovnost.

1687
01:31:33,760 --> 01:31:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] Kako razmišljaš

1688
01:31:36,340 --> 01:31:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] o duhovnosti?

1689
01:31:37,079 --> 01:31:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čuj,

1690
01:31:37,859 --> 01:31:38,600
[SPEAKER_00] ovisno o tome

1691
01:31:38,600 --> 01:31:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] kako razmišljaju

1692
01:31:39,760 --> 01:31:40,939
[SPEAKER_00] drugi ljudi

1693
01:31:40,939 --> 01:31:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] o kojima,

1694
01:31:41,840 --> 01:31:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] o čim vizijama pričamo.

1695
01:31:43,460 --> 01:31:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kako bi se reklo,

1696
01:31:44,180 --> 01:31:44,800
[SPEAKER_00] s jedne strane,

1697
01:31:44,800 --> 01:31:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnost je danas

1698
01:31:46,119 --> 01:31:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] nekakav oblika

1699
01:31:46,859 --> 01:31:47,560
[SPEAKER_00] kao nekakve šatru

1700
01:31:47,560 --> 01:31:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] psihoterapije ponekad.

1701
01:31:48,779 --> 01:31:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je duhovnost

1702
01:31:50,260 --> 01:31:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] nekakav eskapizam.

1703
01:31:51,300 --> 01:31:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pa odlaziš

1704
01:31:52,300 --> 01:31:53,020
[SPEAKER_00] vikendima negdje,

1705
01:31:53,020 --> 01:31:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] pa nešto ti.

1706
01:31:53,680 --> 01:31:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ne promeniš se sebe

1707
01:31:55,239 --> 01:31:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] ni ovoliko.

1708
01:31:55,739 --> 01:31:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ja zapravo ne znam

1709
01:31:58,279 --> 01:31:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] šta je.

1710
01:31:58,920 --> 01:32:00,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je duhovnost

1711
01:32:00,100 --> 01:32:01,180
[SPEAKER_00] u temeljnom obliku

1712
01:32:01,180 --> 01:32:01,859
[SPEAKER_00] život sam.

1713
01:32:01,859 --> 01:32:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to.

1714
01:32:03,239 --> 01:32:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ne treba tebi

1715
01:32:03,720 --> 01:32:04,600
[SPEAKER_00] drugi duhovnosti.

1716
01:32:04,600 --> 01:32:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sve što zagovađaš,

1717
01:32:06,079 --> 01:32:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] što ti se zbiva u životu,

1718
01:32:07,579 --> 01:32:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] zbiva se u tvom duhu.

1719
01:32:08,920 --> 01:32:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] U tome kako ti to življavaš.

1720
01:32:10,199 --> 01:32:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] A kako bi se reklo,

1721
01:32:11,760 --> 01:32:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] to je postoji jedan pojam

1722
01:32:12,619 --> 01:32:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] za jednu subkulturu

1723
01:32:13,960 --> 01:32:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari.

1724
01:32:14,359 --> 01:32:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Koja se temelji

1725
01:32:15,920 --> 01:32:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] na malo retritima,

1726
01:32:17,720 --> 01:32:18,479
[SPEAKER_00] na eskapizmu,

1727
01:32:18,479 --> 01:32:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] na određenim idejama

1728
01:32:19,640 --> 01:32:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] o prehrani,

1729
01:32:20,199 --> 01:32:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] knjigama,

1730
01:32:20,819 --> 01:32:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] meditaciji.

1731
01:32:22,720 --> 01:32:23,859
[SPEAKER_00] nevjerojatno me koliko ljudi

1732
01:32:23,859 --> 01:32:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji se bave takvim vidovima

1733
01:32:25,039 --> 01:32:25,859
[SPEAKER_00] raznih duhovnosti,

1734
01:32:25,859 --> 01:32:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] koliko nesvjesno postaju

1735
01:32:27,460 --> 01:32:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] teški fanatici je.

1736
01:32:29,640 --> 01:32:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] Postaju takvi fanatici

1737
01:32:31,279 --> 01:32:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] da je to nevjerojatno.

1738
01:32:32,739 --> 01:32:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] Drugim rećem,

1739
01:32:34,300 --> 01:32:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] oni su samo jedan set

1740
01:32:35,180 --> 01:32:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] tvrdih uvjerenja

1741
01:32:36,159 --> 01:32:37,399
[SPEAKER_00] zamijenili za drugi.

1742
01:32:37,399 --> 01:32:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što viđamo

1743
01:32:38,579 --> 01:32:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] oko sebe

1744
01:32:39,079 --> 01:32:40,239
[SPEAKER_00] u društvenoj dinamici.

1745
01:32:40,239 --> 01:32:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] I popularnosti.

1746
01:32:41,180 --> 01:32:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pisao sam uvjerenje

1747
